Subject: [PATCH 2/3] feat: page-level visual identity and section design

Home: drifting dot particle layer in hero, mobile-only decorative ring, decorative quote-mark SVG behind instructor section, cursor-glow on hero.
Themes: PhaseIcon next to each phase header + journey progress bar showing position (1/6, 2/6 ...).
Progress: animated progress bars using shimmer gradient fill + completion glow-pulse at 100%, vertical connector line between phases on desktop.
Toolkit: client-side ToolkitFilter with animated pill-style filter buttons + layout animations between filter states.
About: ParallaxSection wrapper on story heading, timeline-style yellow dots for each paragraph, stat-grid-dark with dot-grid backdrop.
